\title{Denotational semantics of the addition language}

\p{The [denotational semantics](plt-semantics-0002) of the [addition
language](plt-languages-0001) is given below:

##{\llbracket \text{Val}\ n \rrbracket = n}
##{\llbracket \text{Add}\ x\ y \rrbracket = \llbracket x \rrbracket + \llbracket y \rrbracket}
}
